METROPOLITAN GROUP PROPERTY AND CASUALTY INSURANCE COMPANY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Kerline JEAN-FRANCOIS, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Marie Jean-Francois, Defendant. C-645 September Term 2018
081902 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005455-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
